{"tid":933691,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"在回家路上","createTime":"2018-12-08T16:47:58.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-08T16:56:56.000Z","uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"27890a742305763b2537c2b21a41959ca521cfdd","tid":933691,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T16:47:58.000Z","msg":"一個人，<br />\n天氣很冷。<br />\n<br />\n呼。<br />\n<br />\n我吹了一口氣，<br />\n低頭在想，<br />\n究竟是什麼原因，<br />\n和女朋友的關係如履薄冰。"},{"pid":"30811240c815f7325e1249ed276f934a2acff937","tid":933691,"uid":74214,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-08T16:56:56.000Z","msg":"「走了。」<br />\n我向她報告行蹤。<br />\n<br />\n十分鐘<br />\n十五分鐘<br />\n二十分鐘<br />\n...<br />\n<br />\n「凍唔凍呀？返屋企小心啲！」<br />\n我期待她的回覆。<br />\n<br />\n但，她沒有。<br />\n<br />\n是看到電話吧，<br />\n只是感情淡了，<br />\n就不會再著緊你的行蹤。<br />\n也懶得去關心你。"}]}